snippet.title: Marshmallow Infinity (v1.1) - Cubee Games
snippet.description:
Leap Year update is now live!


Help Marshmallow survive the factory fire.


Be careful not to get burnt unless you need some extra help getting around ... maybe you should take some damage, he's a marshmallow after all!
